import { library } from '@fortawesome/fontawesome-svg-core'
import { faEye, faEyeSlash, faTimes, faPencilAlt, faCheck, faPlus, faBan, faUndo, faNetworkWired } from '@fortawesome/free-solid-svg-icons'
import { faCheckSquare, faSquare, faClock } from '@fortawesome/free-regular-svg-icons'
 
library.add(faEye, faEyeSlash, faTimes, faPencilAlt, faCheckSquare, faSquare, faCheck, faPlus, faBan, faUndo, faClock, faNetworkWired )
